<p>The Talentless founder also enjoyed the family time, sharing a sweet photo of himself steering the boat with son Reign Aston, five, in his lap.</p>

<p>He's reportedly been focusing on his family, amid his split with girlfriend of three years Sofia Richie, 22, back in May.</p>

