<p>The split came after Scott briefly checked into rehab in Colorado, before leaving a week later over privacy concerns. </p>

<p>Kourtney addresses the scandal in an upcoming episode of Keeping Up with the Kardashians, discussing leaked photos and conversations with his therapist.</p>

<p>She said in a clip from the upcoming season 19: 'I feel like whoever did leak this information should be really ashamed of themselves. Everyone deserves to deal with their past traumas in privacy. He was completely violated.'</p>

